description:
Danny recaps this week's Vanderpump Rules, which features a lot of engagement talk, heartfelt reveals from She-She that are overlooked, plus a shocking scene at Ariana and Tom's pool. On Real Housewives of Atlanta, Kandi and Todd struggle with a work/life balance, while Nene does the robot, and Kenya reveals more about her relationship with M*rc.


RHOA Recap: 38:00ish


YOUTUBE: https://www.youtube.com/dannypellegrino1

For tickets to the Chicago live show: https://bit.ly/3bc6QLX
